---
<MainLayout>

  <HeroSection
    title=`Tank Global<span
        class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400"> Solutions</span>`
    subTitle="Solving all your tank needs. Over 20 years delivering reliable and innovative ISO tank solutions. We are your strategic partner for operations, sales, leasing, and specialized consulting."
    primaryBtn="Start Exploring"
    primaryBtnURL="/services"
    secondaryBtn="Contact Us"
    secondaryBtnURL="/contact"
    withReview={true}
    rating=`<span class="font-bold">4.8</span> / 5`
    starCount={4}
    reviews=`From Over <span class="font-bold">12.8k</span> Reviews`
    src={heroImage}
    alt="Stack of ScrewFast product boxes containing assorted hardware tools"
  />

  <ClientsSection
    title="Trusted by Industry Leaders"
    subTitle="Experience the reliability chosen by industry giants."
    partners={partnersData}
  />

  <FeaturesGeneral
    title="Our Philosophy"
    subTitle="At Tank Global Solutions, we are committed to delivering true value to our clients through precision-engineered ISO tank solutions backed by efficiency and forward-thinking. Our mission is simple: to be the go-to provider of specialized tank solutions that exceed expectations and deliver peace of mind."
